deck_description:
Its literally just Brave Token Dpe Turbo with a Ghostrick engine.

&nbsp;

The deck is very hand trap resilient and can end with Wandering Gryphon Rider + Dpe and/or Utopic Draco Future depending of your matchup and hand.

&nbsp;

The Ghostrick combo:

You start XYZ summoning Ghostrick Alucard with any level 3 mosnters ~XYZ summon Ghostrick Angel of Mischief using Alucard ~Activate Mischief effect, detach Alucard and add Ghostrick Shot to your hand ~Activate Shot and Summon Alucard from your GY ~Summon another Mischief ~XYZ summon Number F0: Utopic Future and then climb it into a Draco Future. The only problem in this combo is that if you draw Ghostrick Shot you can't make it because the Alucard you would need to summon isn't in your GY, you can resolve this poblem by just using another Alucard, but i will keep the engine efficient and small.

&nbsp;

